{{Conservatism}}
'''加拿大保守黨'''（{{lang-en|Conservative Party of Canada}}；{{lang-fr|Parti conservateur du Canada}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]]一個[[中間偏右|中間偏右]]政黨，于2003年12月7日由[[加拿大聯盟|加拿大聯盟]]及[[加拿大進步保守黨|加拿大進步保守黨]]合併而成。自從合併後，「托利黨」（{{lang|en|Tories}}）這個綽號就指加拿大保守黨（之前是進步保守黨的綽號）。該黨現時爲[[加拿大下議院|加拿大下議院]][[官方反對黨_(加拿大)|官方反對黨]]，對上一次執政時期則為2006年至2015年。現任黨魁為[https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Candice_Bergen_(politician) 甘蒂絲·伯根] {{Wayback|url=https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Candice_Bergen_(politician) |date=20220601192428 }}（署理黨魁）。

== 歷史 ==
=== 建立初期 ===
在2003年10月16日，當時兩大反對黨，進步保守黨和加拿大聯盟的黨領[[彼得·麥凱|彼得·麥凱]]及[[斯蒂芬·哈珀|斯蒂芬·哈珀]]宣佈其兩黨合併成為一黨<ref name="CBC031016">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-and-mackay-announce-deal-to-unite-the-right-1.391784 |title=Harper and MacKay announce deal to unite the right |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-10-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153348/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/harper-and-mackay-announce-deal-to-unite-the-right-1.391784 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這項合併於同年12月初獲95%的加拿大聯盟代表和90%的進步保守黨代表投票支持<ref name="CBC060202">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/uniteright_timeline.html |title=Unite the right: Timeline |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2006-02-02 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305225130/http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/conservativeparty/uniteright_timeline.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而加拿大保守黨亦於同月8日正式登記成立<ref name="CBC031216">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservative-party-unveils-new-logo-1.406118 |title=Conservative party unveils new logo |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2015-11-06 |date=2003-12-16 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305153351/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/conservative-party-unveils-new-logo-1.406118 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

部分保守黨黨員一度希望[[安大略省|安大略省]][[安大略省省長|前省長]][[邁克·哈利斯|邁克·哈利斯]]參選黨領，但他則婉拒。此外，其他熱門人選如麥凱、[[紐賓士域|紐賓士域]]省長羅德（{{lang|en|Bernard Lord}}）和[[亞伯達|亞伯達]][[阿爾伯塔省省長|省長]]簡欣（{{lang|en|Ralph Klein}}）亦宣佈不會參選。曾於2003年5月與麥凱爭奪進步保守黨黨領職位的[[彭迪思|彭迪思]]於同年12月中宣布參選，但於2004年1月以經費不足為由宣佈棄選<ref>{{cite news |url=http://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/jim-prentice-a-career-that-changed-conservative-politics |title=Jim Prentice: A career that changed Conservative politics |publisher=《卡加利先驅報》 |accessdate=2016-10-14 |date=2016-10-14 |author=Wood, James |coauthor=Varcoe, Chris |archive-date=2016-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017090340/http://calgaryherald.com/news/politics/jim-prentice-a-career-that-changed-conservative-politics |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最後共有三人參選保守黨黨領，分別為哈珀、前[[安大略進步保守黨|安大略進步保守黨]]內閣成員[[甘禮明|甘禮明]]及[[麥格納|麥格納國際公司]]行政總裁[[貝琳達·施特羅那赫|貝琳達·施特羅那赫]]。在2004年3月20日舉行的黨領選舉中，哈珀在首輪投票獲得68.9%選票（67143票），壓倒施特羅那赫（22.9%、22286票）和甘禮明（8.2%、7968票）當選加拿大保守黨黨領<ref>Tom Flanagan, ''Harper's Team''. Montreal & Kingston: McGill-Queen’s University Press, 2007, pg. 133</ref>。

=== 哈珀時期 ===
[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]籍[[加拿大總理|總理]][[保羅·馬丁|保羅·馬丁]]於2004年5月（即哈珀當選保守黨黨領後兩個月）宣布解散國會，並於同年6月28日舉行[[2004年加拿大联邦大选|聯邦大選]]。保守黨在哈珀領導下贏得[[加拿大眾議院|眾議院]]99個議席，而自由黨則贏取135席並失去其多數政府地位，只能以少數姿態繼續執政。

期間自由黨捲入貪腐醜聞（即「贊助醜聞」），令該黨支持度下滑。葉素斯列特（{{lang|en|Ipsos-Reid}}）在戈梅利委員會（{{lang|en|Gomery Commission}}）首份調查報告公開後進行的民調顯示保守黨和自由黨的支持度不相伯仲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ipsos-na.com/news/pressrelease.cfm?id=2857|title=Grits Thrashed in Wake of Gomery Report|publisher=Ipsos-na.com|date=2005-11-04|accessdate=2010-04-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090212003018/http://www.ipsos-na.com/news/pressrelease.cfm?id=2857|archivedate=2009-02-12}}</ref>。2005年11月24日，哈珀在眾議院向執政自由黨政府提出[[不信任動議|不信任動議]]，在另外兩個反對黨[[魁人政團|魁人政團]]和[[加拿大新民主黨|新民主黨]]的支持下於同月28日通過，自由黨少數政府遂告倒台，新一場聯邦大選則定於2006年1月23日舉行。

保守黨在2006年聯邦大選中贏取眾議院308席中的124席，較自由黨的103席為多，藉此以少數政府姿態上台執政。該屆國會會期差不多長達三年，是加拿大歷來任期最長的少數政府<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www2.parl.gc.ca/parlinfo/compilations/parliament/DurationMinorityGovernment.aspx |title=Duration of Minority Governments |author= |date=2008-11-18 |publisher=Parliament of Canada |accessdate=2011-03-23 |archive-date=2013-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130507070220/http://www.parl.gc.ca/ParlInfo/compilations/parliament/DurationMinorityGovernment.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

保守黨在[[2008年加拿大联邦大选|2008年聯邦大選]]中再次贏得最多議席，但仍未奪得下議院過半數席位，哈珀因此第二度執掌少數政府。

2008年大選舉行六個星期後，[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]和[[加拿大新民主黨|新民主黨]]已部署向保守黨少數政府提出不信任動議。面對兩個反對黨夾攻，總理哈珀於2008年12月4日向時任總督[[莊美楷|莊美楷]]提請將國會休會至2009年1月26日<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2008/12/04/harper-jean.html|title=GG agrees to suspend Parliament: Harper|publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC]]|date=2008-12-04|accessdate=2008-12-04|archive-date=2008-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205134535/http://www.cbc.ca/canada/story/2008/12/04/harper-jean.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，[[葉禮庭|葉禮庭]]接替[[斯特凡·迪翁|迪安]]出任自由黨黨領後，自由黨改變初衷，在國會復會後取消提出不信任動議的計劃<ref name="theglobeandmail.com">{{cite news |author=Canada |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20090128.wPOLbudget0128/BNStory/politics/home?cid=al_gam_mostemail |title=Ignatieff okays budget, with conditions |publisher=The Globe and Mail |date= |accessdate=2010-04-23 |archive-date=2009-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090308090940/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/story/RTGAM.20090128.wPOLbudget0128/BNStory/politics/home?cid=al_gam_mostemail |dead-url=no }}</ref>，保守黨少數政府因此得以繼續執政。自由黨再於2009年10月向保守黨政府提出不信任動議，但動議在新民主黨議員投棄權票的情況下被否決。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idCATRE58T4BE20091001?sp=true|title=Canada's government survives non-confidence motion|date=2009-10-01|accessdate=2013-04-28|archive-date=2012-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329064815/http://ca.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idCATRE58T4BE20091001?sp=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年，加拿大選舉局落案控告四名保守黨黨員，指他們在2006年聯邦大選競選活動期間超出法定競選開支上限，因而違反加拿大選舉法<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.elections.ca/content.aspx?section=abo&dir=com/stat&document=index&lang=e |title=''Canada Elections Act'' Charges Laid |publisher=Elections Canada |accessdate=2011-04-27 |date=2011-02-25 |archive-date=2019-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611213606/https://www.elections.ca/content.aspx?section=abo&dir=com%2Fstat&document=index&lang=e |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Akin |first=David |url=http://www.lfpress.com/news/canada/2011/02/24/17401196.html |title=PM shrugs off charges against Tories |publisher=Lfpress.com |date=2011-02-25 |accessdate=2011-04-17 |archive-date=2013-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609133317/http://www.lfpress.com/news/canada/2011/02/24/17401196.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=illegal>{{cite news |author=Bruce Cheadle |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/tory-election-allegations-illegal-not-administrative-prosecutor-says/article1924161/ |title=Tory election allegations 'illegal' not administrative, prosecutor says |publisher=The Globe and Mail |date=2011-02-28 |accessdate=2011-04-17 |archive-date=2013-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425180911/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/tory-election-allegations-illegal-not-administrative-prosecutor-says/article1924161/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另一方面，[[加拿大國會下議院議長|下議院議長]]梅里根（{{lang|en|Peter Milliken}}）於2011年3月9日裁定國際合作部長小田（{{lang|en|Bev Oda}}）因更改政府文件而誤導國會，而哈珀政府亦拒絕全面透露多項政策的細節和費用預估<ref name=findings>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/21/pol-privilege-contempt.html |title=MPs' report finds government in contempt |author= |date=2011-03-21 |work= |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2011-03-24 |archive-date=2011-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110324122405/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/21/pol-privilege-contempt.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，兩者因此違反國會特權並面臨蔑視國會的控訴<ref>{{cite news |title=PM on rulings: 'win some, lose some' |author=Laura Payton |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/09/pol-speaker-rulings.html |newspaper=CBC News |date=2011-03-09 |accessdate=2011-03-26 |archive-date=2013-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130323212231/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/09/pol-speaker-rulings.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。梅里根將此兩項議題交予國會委員會審議，並將委員會呈交報告的限期定為同年3月21日，即保守黨政府公佈財政預算案的前夕。委員會裁定哈珀政府蔑視國會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www2.parl.gc.ca/content/hoc/Committee/403/PROC/Reports/RP5047570/procrp27/procrp27-e.pdf |title=Question of Privilege Relating to the Failure of the Government To Fully Provide the Documents as Ordered by the House: Report of the Standing Committee on Procedure and House Affairs |accessdate=2011-04-26 |date=March 2011}}</ref>，自由黨因此向哈珀政府提出不信任動議<ref>{{cite news |author=Stephanie Levitz and Martin O'Hanlon, The Canadian Press: |url=http://www.globaltvcalgary.com/personalities/Liberals+introduce+confidence+motion/4489986/story.html |title=Harper government set to fall Friday, setting stage for vote in early May |publisher=Globaltvcalgary.com |date=2011-03-23 |accessdate=2011-04-13 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822083926/https://globalnews.ca/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。下議院於3月25日以156票對145票通過動議<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/25/pol-defeat.html |title=MPs gather for historic vote |author=CBC News |publisher=[[Canadian_Broadcasting_Corporation|CBC]] |date=2011-03-25 |accessdate=2011-03-25 |archive-date=2011-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110328021055/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/03/25/pol-defeat.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Mayeda|first=Andrew|title=Harper government falls|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/Harper+government+falls/4503131/story.html|accessdate=2011-03-25|newspaper=Vancouver Sun|date=2011-03-25}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，哈珀領導的少數政府因而倒台。

{{main|2011年加拿大联邦大选}}
2011年3月25日，[[加拿大自由党|自由党]]向哈珀政府提出不信任動議，[[加拿大下議院|加拿大下議院]]以156票贊成，145票反對通过对哈珀总理领导的保守党少数政府的不信任動議，使之成为加历史上首个因“藐视议会”而下台的政府。加拿大总督[[大衛·勞埃德·約翰斯頓|戴维·约翰斯顿]]次日批准解散第40届议会。

加拿大第41届联邦大选初步统计结果5月2日晚揭晓，哈珀领导的保守党获得胜利，实现连续三届执政，并在总计308个选区中的166个选区获胜，超过了上届的143个选区，最重要的是超过了组成多数政府所需的155个选区，成功籌組23年來首個由保守黨領導的多數政府。保守党领袖哈珀在自己所屬的卡尔加里选区发表获胜感言时说，选民的支持使加拿大摆脱了持续不断举行选举的困局，掀开了稳定发展的新篇章。

=== 官方反對黨 ===
{{main|2015年加拿大联邦大选}}
2015年10月19日舉行的大選中，保守黨僅取得99個席位，落敗於[[賈斯汀·杜魯多|賈斯汀·杜魯多]]領導的[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]，[[史蒂芬·哈珀|哈珀]]亦爲敗選負責而宣佈辭去黨領職務，結束12年的黨領生涯。保守黨黨團於2015年11月5日選出[[羅娜·安布羅斯|羅娜·安布羅斯]]爲臨時黨領<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conservative-interim-leader-vote-1.3306152|title=Conservatives choose Alberta MP Rona Ambrose as interim leader|work=cbc.ca|accessdate=2016-10-13|archive-date=2017-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170721035412/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conservative-interim-leader-vote-1.3306152|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rcinet.ca/en/2015/11/05/rona-ambrose-elected-interim-conservative-leader/|title=Rona Ambrose elected interim Conservative leader|first=Radio Canada|last=International|work=rcinet.ca|accessdate=2016-12-21|archive-date=2017-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609143523/http://www.rcinet.ca/en/2015/11/05/rona-ambrose-elected-interim-conservative-leader/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2017年5月27日舉行的{{le|保守黨黨領選舉|2017 Conservative Party of Canada leadership election}}中，[[安德魯·熙爾|安德魯·熙爾]]經過13輪投票後當選<ref name="星島170528">{{cite news |url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/1777127/2017-05-28/post-%E9%81%B8%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E5%8D%9E%E8%81%B6%E7%88%BE%E9%80%A3%E8%B4%8F12%E8%BC%AA%E5%B0%BE%E8%BC%AA%E5%BE%AE%E8%BC%B8-38%E6%AD%B2%E3%80%8C%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%88%E5%93%88%E7%8F%80%E3%80%8D/?variant=zh-hk |title=選前大熱卞聶爾連贏12輪尾輪微輸 38歲「翻版哈珀」 爆冷當選保守黨領 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加東版 |date=2017-05-28 |accessdate=2017-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602113622/http://toronto.singtao.ca/1777127/2017-05-28/post-%E9%81%B8%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E5%8D%9E%E8%81%B6%E7%88%BE%E9%80%A3%E8%B4%8F12%E8%BC%AA%E5%B0%BE%E8%BC%AA%E5%BE%AE%E8%BC%B8-38%E6%AD%B2%E3%80%8C%E7%BF%BB%E7%89%88%E5%93%88%E7%8F%80%E3%80%8D/?variant=zh-hk |archive-date=2017-06-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

{{main|2019年加拿大联邦大选}}
執政自由黨於2019年捲入[[SNC－蘭萬靈事件|SNC－蘭萬靈事件]]後，一度惠及保守黨在[[2019年加拿大聯邦大選|同年聯邦大選]]的勝算。保守黨在該屆大選增添22個議席，得票比率也為眾黨之最，但自由黨最終仍贏取少數政府地位繼續執政。另一方面，[[加拿大廣播公司|加拿大廣播公司]]報道指保守黨支付熙爾子女私校的部分學費，惹來爭議。面對黨內壓力，熙爾於同年12月宣布辭任保守黨黨領<ref>{{cite web |title=Canada Conservative leader in surprise resignation |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-50762474 |website=BBC News |date=2019-12-12 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624103218/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-50762474 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Rabson |first1=Mia |first2= |title=Conservative party in disarray over Scheer private school controversy |url=https://www.nationalobserver.com/2019/12/15/news/conservative-party-disarray-over-scheer-private-school-controversy |website=National Observer |language=en |date=2019-12-15 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200624010441/https://www.nationalobserver.com/2019/12/15/news/conservative-party-disarray-over-scheer-private-school-controversy |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=MacCharles |first1=Tonda |title=Andrew Scheer quitting as Conservative leader amid controversy |url=https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2019/12/12/andrew-scheer-to-step-down-as-conservative-party-leader.html |website=thestar.com |language=en |date=2019-12-12 |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806043149/https://www.thestar.com/politics/federal/2019/12/12/andrew-scheer-to-step-down-as-conservative-party-leader.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但留任至新任黨領當選為止<ref>{{cite web |last1=Connolly |first1=Amanda |title=Conservative Leader Andrew Scheer resigns, vows to stay on until new leader chosen |url=https://globalnews.ca/news/6288286/andrew-scheer-resignation/ |website=Global News |accessdate=2020-08-25 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925195209/https://globalnews.ca/news/6288286/andrew-scheer-resignation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2020年8月舉行的{{le|保守黨黨領選舉|2020 Conservative Party of Canada leadership election}}中，[[艾林·奧圖爾|艾林·奧圖爾]]經過3輪投票後當選。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Erin O'Toole wins Conservative leadership race on the third ballot|url=https://nationalpost.com/news/politics/erin-otoole-wins-conservative-leadership-race-on-the-third-ballot|access-date=2020-08-24|website=National Post|language=en-CA|archive-date=2021-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815154545/https://nationalpost.com/news/politics/erin-otoole-wins-conservative-leadership-race-on-the-third-ballot}}</ref>

{{main|2021年加拿大联邦大选}}
杜魯多解散國會觸發了2021年9月的聯邦選舉，希望贏得多數政府，儘管在競選過程中，奧圖爾的保守黨在民調中領先自由黨。保守黨亦面對右翼[[加拿大人民黨|人民黨]]挑戰。奧圖爾於競選期尾段向人民黨支持者拉票，謂人民黨會分薄右翼票源，最終只惠及自由黨<ref name=cbc092021/>。保守黨在該屆大選再次敗予自由黨，但得票率則高於自由黨，而奧圖爾本人則再度在杜林選區連任眾議院議員<ref name="ctv092121">{{cite news |last1=Turnbull |first1=Sarah |title=Conservatives fail to dethrone Liberals |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/federal-election-2021/conservatives-fail-to-dethrone-liberals-1.5593607 |access-date=2021-09-21 |work=CTV News |publisher=Bell Media |date=2021-09-21 |archive-date=2022-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531061002/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/federal-election-2021/conservatives-fail-to-dethrone-liberals-1.5593607 }}</ref><ref name="popvote21">{{cite news |last1=Flanagan |first1=Ryan |title=Liberals return to Alberta, and 5 other surprises in the election results |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/federal-election-2021/liberals-return-to-alberta-and-5-other-surprises-in-the-election-results-1.5593768 |access-date=2021-09-21 |work=CTV News |publisher=Bell Media |date=2021-09-21 |archive-date=2022-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531055928/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/federal-election-2021/liberals-return-to-alberta-and-5-other-surprises-in-the-election-results-1.5593768 }}</ref>。他於大選當晚表示會留任黨魁<ref name="cbc092021">{{cite news |last1=Tunney |first1=Catharine |title=Conservative Leader Erin O'Toole sticks with moderate message despite falling short |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-election-1.6182500 |access-date=2021-09-21 |work=CBC News |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=2021-09-20 |archive-date=2022-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531004235/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-election-1.6182500 }}</ref>，但其後保守黨内部則就奧圖爾去留出現分歧<ref name="ctv092621">{{cite news |last1=Turnbull |first1=Sarah |title=Conservatives divided on fate of O'Toole, as party's MPs call for unity |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/conservatives-divided-on-fate-of-o-toole-as-party-s-mps-call-for-unity-1.5599886 |access-date=2021-09-26 |work=CTV News |publisher=Bell Media |date=2021-09-26 |archive-date=2022-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531150345/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/conservatives-divided-on-fate-of-o-toole-as-party-s-mps-call-for-unity-1.5599886 }}</ref><ref name="cbc092321">{{cite news |last1=Tasker |first1=John Paul |title=Conservatives divided on what to do about Erin O'Toole after election loss |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conseratives-split-erin-otoole-1.6187155 |access-date=2021-09-26 |work=CBC News |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=2021-09-23 |archive-date=2022-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220204020521/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/conseratives-split-erin-otoole-1.6187155 }}</ref>。但最終與2019年大選類似，保守黨再次贏得得票比率，但未能獲得最多席位，從而使賈斯汀·特魯多領導下的自由黨能夠組建另一個少數派政府。2022年1月31日，卡加利地區保守黨籍國會議員本森（{{lang|en|Bob Benzen}}）致函保守黨黨團主席里德（{{lang|en|Scott Reid}}）要求舉行黨魁檢討選舉，並獲35名保守黨籍國會議員署名支持<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tasker |first1=John |title=Conservative caucus revolt triggers vote on Erin O'Toole's leadership |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-leadership-review-caucus-1.6334491 |website=CBC News |access-date=2022-02-02 |date=2022-01-31 |archive-date=2022-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220204032050/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/erin-otoole-leadership-review-caucus-1.6334491 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=35保守黨國會議員連署 迫使奧圖爾面臨信任投票 |url=https://www.singtao.ca/5540865/2022-02-01/post-35%e4%bf%9d%e5%ae%88%e9%bb%a8%e5%9c%8b%e6%9c%83%e8%ad%b0%e5%93%a1%e9%80%a3%e7%bd%b2-%e8%bf%ab%e4%bd%bf%e5%a5%a7%e5%9c%96%e7%88%be%e9%9d%a2%e8%87%a8%e4%bf%a1%e4%bb%bb%e6%8a%95%e7%a5%a8/ |publisher=《星島日報》加東版 |access-date=2022-02-05 |date=2022-02-01 }}</ref>。經過秘密投票後，保守黨黨團以73票對45票通過罷免奧圖爾<ref>{{Cite news|last=Tasker|first=John Paul|date=2022-02-02|title=Conservative MPs vote to remove Erin O'Toole as leader|work=CBC News|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/otoole-lea