e=奧圖爾遭罷免 女副手暫接掌 |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20220203/vaa1h_r.htm |publisher=《明報》加西網 |access-date=2022-02-05 |date=2022-02-03 |archive-date=2022-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217005211/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/VAN/htm/NEWS/20220203/vaa1h_r.htm }}</ref>。

{{main|{{le|第45屆加拿大联邦大选|45th Canadian federal election}}}}
伯根作為臨時黨魁的職位將只持續幾個月<ref>{{cite web |last1=Turnbull |first1=Sarah |title=Bergen says she will work to 'strengthen' conservative movement as interim leader |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/bergen-says-she-will-work-to-strengthen-conservative-movement-as-interim-leader-1.5765926 |website=CTV News |access-date=2022-02-06 |date=2022-02-03 |quote=Over the next few months, my colleagues and I will be listening and acting. |archive-date=2022-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220531061002/https://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/bergen-says-she-will-work-to-strengthen-conservative-movement-as-interim-leader-1.5765926 }}</ref>，新的黨魁將於9月10日舉行的{{le|保守黨黨魁選舉|2022 Conservative Party of Canada leadership election}}選出<ref>{{cite news |title=Federal Conservatives to choose new leader Sept. 10 |url=https://toronto.citynews.ca/2022/03/02/tories-choose-new-leader-sept-10/ |publisher=CityNews |access-date=2022-03-11 |date=2022-03-02 |archive-date=2022-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220303033839/https://toronto.citynews.ca/2022/03/02/tories-choose-new-leader-sept-10/ }}</ref>。目前參選黨魁選舉的有[[溥禮瑞|溥禮瑞]]<ref>{{cite news |title=保守黨黨魁選舉未正式開鑼 僅溥禮瑞明確表態有意參選 |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20220208/tdd1_r.htm |publisher=《明報》加東網 |access-date=2022-03-11 |date=2022-02-08 |archive-date=2022-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524000230/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20220208/tdd1_r.htm }}</ref>、{{le|劉易斯|Leslyn Lewis}}、[[莊社理|莊社理]]<ref>{{cite news |title=劉易斯再競逐聯邦保守黨領袖莊社理彭建邦傳本周加入戰團 |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20220309/vab2_r.htm |publisher=《明報》 |access-date=2022-03-11 |date=2022-03-09 |archive-date=2022-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220514092722/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20220309/vab2_r.htm }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Jean Charest confirms he's running to lead the Conservative Party |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jean-charest-conservative-leadership-1.6378920 |work=CBC News |access-date=2022-03-11 |date=2022-03-09 |archive-date=2022-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220309210644/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jean-charest-conservative-leadership-1.6378920 }}</ref>、巴伯 (Roman Baber)<ref>{{cite news |title=Independent Ontario MPP Roman Baber to enter Conservative party leadership race |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/roman-baber-enters-conservative-party-leadership-race-1.6378234 |work=CBC News |access-date=2022-03-11 |date=2022-03-09 |archive-date=2022-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220309142942/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/roman-baber-enters-conservative-party-leadership-race-1.6378234 }}</ref>、[[彭建邦|彭建邦]]<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-03-13 |title=Patrick Brown, mayor of Brampton, Ont., joins race to lead federal Conservatives |url=https://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/patrick-brown-mayor-of-brampton-ont-joins-race-to-lead-federal-conservatives-1.5817416 |access-date=2022-03-15 |website=CTVNews |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220313154021/https://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/patrick-brown-mayor-of-brampton-ont-joins-race-to-lead-federal-conservatives-1.5817416 }}</ref>和{{le|艾齊森|Scott Aitchison}}，其中溥禮瑞 (Pierre Poilievre) 為大熱人選<ref>{{cite news |title=Pierre Poilievre the favourite among Conservative voters to lead party in next election, poll finds|url=https://nationalpost.com/news/pierre-poilievre-is-the-favourite-among-conservative-voters-to-lead-party-in-next-election-poll-finds |work=National Post |access-date=2022-03-11 |date=2022-03-10}}</ref>。

== 政治觀點與立場 ==
作為一個保守派政黨，保守黨傾向低稅、[[小政府|小政府]]、对犯罪持強硬態度、保持及增强军力、反對[[堕胎|堕胎]]、反對[[賣淫|賣淫]]的合法化。身為加拿大聯盟的後繼者，保守黨還支持改革上議院，支持「選舉、均等、有效」的上議院，並加強[[加拿大總理|加拿大總理]]的權力。保守黨也反對[[大麻|大麻]]合法化。

=== 2006年聯邦大選 ===
保守黨於[[2006年加拿大联邦大选|2006年聯邦大選]]期間提出的政綱：
*選舉後縮減物品及服務稅7%至6%，然後5%。
*建立檢舉[[逃漏稅|逃漏稅]]的獎勵制度
*支持及改革「傳統[[工業|工業]]」，包括[[農業|農業]]、[[漁業|漁業]]、[[礦業|礦業]]
*制定各種罪行最少的監禁時間，及在某些情況下結束軟禁。
*增加一個[[DNA|DNA]]資料庫，以防犯性騷擾；提高承諾年齡由14至16歲；向[[兒童色情|兒童色情]]採強硬的態度
*加強疆界、海港及飛機場的保安
*停止登記新的槍械執照；使用節餘雇用更多[[警察|警察]]
*每月給每位低於6歲兒童的家長100元，作為國家兒童保健服務
*增加退休金所得稅
*縮減[[醫院|醫院]]等候的時間
*投資在運輸基礎設施上；為月度運輸通行證介紹減稅
*保衛地方產業，反對對外[[貿易|貿易]]挑戰
*加強與鄰國[[美國|美國]]的關係

